cat: category id of the category for the channels used for tracking, you can find this by enabling developer mode shown in this video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RI3_Z0AEMck then right clicking the category and copying the id.
serverid: main server id, you can find this by following this video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RI3_Z0AEMck
token: discord bot token, if you can't get your follow this: https://discordpy.readthedocs.io/en/latest/discord.html
